{"tid":352660,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇結左婚既巴打分享下？","createTime":"2017-08-09T02:40:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T00:13:42.000Z","uid":23197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"855e49abb7dbb9295c8a1402a981bde195d7b0d5","tid":352660,"uid":23197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T02:40:37.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打結左婚後變到同老婆冇晒感情？<br />\n<br />\n你地會點處理段關係？ 你或者你老婆有冇外遇？<br />\n<br />\n係咪純粹為小朋友先繼續一齊？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打可以分享下"},{"pid":"1e21d083f466a01cf7037a5d71568a98eacccc6b","tid":352660,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T02:48:51.000Z","msg":"同問，各位巴打，如果條女當初唔結婚都冇所謂，你哋會唔會結婚，有冇後悔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a89fb086b1b9945b64c4c38529c48fcb20fec4","tid":352660,"uid":23197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T02:51:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同問，各位巴打，如果條女當初唔結婚都冇所謂，你哋會唔會結婚，有冇後悔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗好少女仔會肯唔結婚"},{"pid":"77404ac761c3f4afc66d60d376e812e330e62f08","tid":352660,"uid":23197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T03:46:18.000Z","msg":"連登得後生巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"640973619ee8f7c794bf5c8e837312ab35158af0","tid":352660,"uid":133205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:58:41.000Z","msg":"咁結黎做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"122cf845846e756c252ef42e0336fc0824953f14","tid":352660,"uid":122639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:28:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登得後生巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點敢覆你啊唔驚俾老婆小咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d9231fe9c1a2ccbcf0f4ff0b729f1093a9d349a","tid":352660,"uid":17633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T07:09:50.000Z","msg":"不如你講多啲<br />\n你依家同你老婆冇晒感情？"},{"pid":"5cffdb1346b7924395b9a21bccecb3137b13112d","tid":352660,"uid":24854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T07:27:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d00acb108e66a519746fda1e052504963b4debc3","tid":352660,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T07:28:12.000Z","msg":"點會冇"},{"pid":"f31efa367e40be5b32081be24ed9cb513687a55b","tid":352660,"uid":131312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T07:32:30.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n<br />\n結左唔夠一年"},{"pid":"3f5ca2142936f8daade551bceb1084088c2c0b71","tid":352660,"uid":23197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T11:30:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名<br />\n<br />\n結左唔夠一年</blockquote><br />\n怕唔怕有呢啲問題？"},{"pid":"0baafa2b86eb5b19e6ee65611db0c9f579097c94","tid":352660,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T11:31:15.000Z","msg":"始亂終棄"},{"pid":"ac0e71d7da78c38d6214a568fda62a0a4950427e","tid":352660,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T11:34:44.000Z","msg":"就結<br />\n同居左大約3年<br />\n留名學野"},{"pid":"db6ef32923c09014b6feede0ac1ff159a01e3e4c","tid":352660,"uid":119367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T11:41:55.000Z","msg":"點解會結左先冇感情？未結之前又冇野？如果未結之前已經淡咁係你拖住人姐"},{"pid":"1f34cb8e4d1d08da50215c4a8352320c1558a3c1","tid":352660,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T11:48:40.000Z","msg":"你地係拍咗幾耐拖先結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結完係兩個人一齊住私樓/租屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6015868de071f706726993ece54ff347a991f5e8","tid":352660,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T11:50:49.000Z","msg":"你地係拍咗幾耐拖先結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結完係兩個人一齊住私樓/租屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95cc02f31fe4b7478c5757902169df98b00e1f59","tid":352660,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T11:51:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解會結左先冇感情？未結之前又冇野？如果未結之前已經淡咁係你拖住人姐</blockquote><br />\n其實唔係無感情 係變左親情<br />\n會無左拍拖嗰種激情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就好似未結之前會車震下<br />\n但結左後就係屋企是但屌下就算？"},{"pid":"8312d8d75aa071bb3134c2c2ffc3af94c2af61ec","tid":352660,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T11:53:23.000Z","msg":"無仔女就分啦<br />\n<br />\n因誤會而結合<br />\n因了解而分開"},{"pid":"4592227435aaa33eeece529b7cf94e2c5c909419","tid":352660,"uid":30438,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T14:48:05.000Z","msg":"巴打你係結左婚有依個煩惱 定<br />\n即將結婚怕有依個煩惱？<br />\n如果你係未結婚就已經諗緊第時會有依d問題<br />\n我勸你諗清楚先啦 <br />\n睇嚟你似對依段感情嘅信心唔大<br />\n做左决定大家就一世㗎啦"},{"pid":"1f3ed11772aa626be5f1f749f442cce2a2c781ff","tid":352660,"uid":23197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T17:14:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打你係結左婚有依個煩惱 定<br />\n即將結婚怕有依個煩惱？<br />\n如果你係未結婚就已經諗緊第時會有依d問題<br />\n我勸你諗清楚先啦 <br />\n睇嚟你似對依段感情嘅信心唔大<br />\n做左决定大家就一世㗎啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以我先想睇下有冇巴打可以分享下"},{"pid":"0cb9727eab9d0943a538493dd186cd8ec239f5b0","tid":352660,"uid":30438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T00:13:42.000Z","msg":"如果我同你講我結左婚之後仲恩愛咗，<br />\n如膠似漆咁<br />\n你會唔會因為我呢句而即刻結婚？<br />\n唔會啊嘛！<br />\n根本呢啲就好personal<br />\n如果你嘅前設已經覺得結左婚就有呢啲問題<br />\n其實根本外人講咩都係廢嘅<br />\n講到底你對依個人已經係邊緣狀態<br />\n諗清楚，唔好害人啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}